<title type="html"><![CDATA[11/10 (Thu) Online Job Application/ Taiwan Sees Rise in Cram School Popularity (Host: Gal)]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/viewtopic.php?t=669&amp;p=697#p697"><![CDATA[
11/10(Thu)  Online Job Application/ Taiwan Sees Rise in Cram School Popularity (Host: Gal)<br /><br />Agenda:<br />7:00-7:10 pm Opening Remarks<br />7:05-7:40 pm Session 1: Group Discussion<br />7:40-8:00 pm Individual Presentation<br />8:00-8:05 pm Break<br />8:05-8:40 pm Session 2: Group Discussion<br />8:40-9:00 pm Individual Presentation<br /><br />We will hold a zoom meeting only.<br /><br />Zoom meeting: Please click the link below<br /><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://zoomtw.zoom.us/j/92987266213?pw">https://zoomtw.zoom.us/j/92987266213?pw</a><!-- m --> ...<br />Meeting ID:929 8726 6213<br />Password:112233<br /><br />-------------------------------------------- <br /><br />Session 1: Online Job Application<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NTIBXS7pbBs&amp;list=WL&amp;index=90">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NTIBXS7 ... L&amp;index=90</a><!-- m --><br /><br />Questions<br />1. Do you have any experience for applying jobs or to interview employees?<br />2. According to your experience, what’s the key point to make it work?<br />3. As you see, will it be easier or tougher to find a new job at post-pandemic era?<br />4. Do you have any suggestion about looking for a second career?<br /><br /><br />Session 2: Taiwan Sees Rise in Cram School Popularity<br /><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RoK7L0i4fvE&amp;list=WL&amp;index=91&amp;t=28s">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RoK7L0i ... x=91&amp;t=28s</a><!-- m --><br /><br />Questions:<br /><br />1. How about your understanding for Taiwanese educational system? <br />2. Do you think it’s good or any aspect to improve?<br />3. How about your understanding for cram school in Taiwan?<br />4. More and more parents prevent their kids from approaching 3C products with pushing them to after-school club or private school.  What’s the advantage and disadvantage in your opinion?<br /><br /><br />P.S.<br />1.參加三次(含實體及線上會議)後，只要繳交1,000元(學生500元)，即可成為ROYAL終身會員!<br />2.請帶著開放的心與熱情來參加全英文會話聚會!<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=38674">Louie Wang</a> — Fri Nov 04, 2022 9:55 pm</p><hr />
